{"tid":474322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★扶貧？羅致光：構思為受惠兒童提供平板電腦","createTime":"2017-11-20T05:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T16:44:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1a922dc15032ff1c12302d85fb5fbf2fff89646f","tid":474322,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，政府高估低收入在職家庭津貼的受惠人數，去年的扶貧措施效果不明顯。他強調政府扶貧不是「愈扶愈貧」，但扶貧工作可以增加，會向着在職貧窮和長者方向做，包括改良低津。<br />\n<br />\n對於有組織的調查指，低津家庭的兒童津貼，被用於補貼居所租金，羅致光在電台節目回應說，低津將會加碼，希望家庭津貼可以幫補，正在構思為受惠兒童<span style=\"color: red;\">提供平板電腦</span>，配合學校電子學習。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1365763-20171120.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1365763-20171120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=s5%2BDHZkeGHiw0ctAYStYK4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5021e8cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1365763-20171120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=917caf6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1365763-20171120.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8e680c6d9ce93ba8c3700754a4a072e563356ec8","tid":474322,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"why not iphoneX<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1ec0992f17ef95044c3346ef94909bd9e0885e","tid":474322,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"買ipad5果啲有限錢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b26d7bafaaa3bd5d3a32353db421169ed426f1","tid":474322,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"ipad pro?<br />\n<br />\nsamsung tab s3?"},{"pid":"4e16596eab26ea24e4bc79fae16ab0ce4fffe756","tid":474322,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":